com.smartsockets
Class TipcCb

java.lang.Object
  com.smartsockets.TipcCb
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.smartsockets.SortableItem
public class TipcCb
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.smartsockets.SortableItem

Holds a reference to a callback entry. This class cannot be directly created by the user. Instead, instances are returned when adding, looking up, and destroying callbacks from the TipcConnClient and TipcSrv classes. This class allows the properties of the callback to be altered.
